09/04/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- Minister of Public Order Luan Rama met on Tuesday (8 April) with Italian Interior Minister Giuseppe Pisanu, who praised efforts by Albanian authorities in the fight against trafficking. Pisanu expressed hope that the co-operation between the two countries in the fight against crime and trafficking would deepen. A day earlier, a joint operation by Italian and Albanian police forces broke up a child trafficking network. (ATA, AGI - 08/04/03)
